    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 6900.0,
      "end_time": 9600.0,
      "text": "Solution, Suspension and Colloid."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 57200.0,
      "end_time": 58700.0,
      "text": "After sometime."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 77900.0,
      "end_time": 80500.0,
      "text": "Let us understand this with the help of an activity."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 92300.0,
      "end_time": 95000.0,
      "text": "Take some water in 3 separate beakers."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 96800.0,
      "end_time": 102000.0,
      "text": "Sugar."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 103000.0,
      "end_time": 104300.0,
      "text": "Lemonade."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 112200.0,
      "end_time": 117100.0,
      "text": "Add sugar in the 1st beaker."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 121800.0,
      "end_time": 123800.0,
      "text": "Lemon?"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 137000.0,
      "end_time": 141000.0,
      "text": "Add chalk powder in the 2nd beaker."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 145200.0,
      "end_time": 149080.0,
      "text": "Add milk in the 3rd beaker."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 157000.0,
      "end_time": 168080.0,
      "text": "Stir all the mixtures."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 182800.0,
      "end_time": 185900.0,
      "text": "Direct a beam of light through each beaker."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 187800.0,
      "end_time": 192400.0,
      "text": "The particles of sugar have completely disappeared in the mixture."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 193000.0,
      "end_time": 194800.0,
      "text": "Such a mixture is called a homogeneous mixture."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 195300.0,
      "end_time": 198200.0,
      "text": "Homogeneous means consistent or uniform throughout."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 199000.0,
      "end_time": 202800.0,
      "text": "The particles of sugar are very small."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 203000.0,
      "end_time": 205400.0,
      "text": "They cannot scatter any light."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 205600.0,
      "end_time": 210600.0,
      "text": "Hence, we are unable to see the path of light inside the Homogeneous mixture."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 211400.0,
      "end_time": 214100.0,
      "text": "Such a mixture is called a solution."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 214900.0,
      "end_time": 220800.0,
      "text": "The size of particles in a solution is usually less than 1 nm."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 223600.0,
      "end_time": 227800.0,
      "text": "We can observe some chalk particles freely moving in the 2nd mixture."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 228700.0,
      "end_time": 231000.0,
      "text": "Such a mixture is called a heterogeneous mixture."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 231400.0,
      "end_time": 234600.0,
      "text": "Heterogeneous means non-uniform."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 235600.0,
      "end_time": 237800.0,
      "text": "Light is directed through the 2nd beaker."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 238400.0,
      "end_time": 243000.0,
      "text": "Here, the path of light is visible inside the heterogeneous mixture."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 243900.0,
      "end_time": 251500.0,
      "text": "The particles of chalk are insoluble in water and are big enough to scatter the light passing through them."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 252300.0,
      "end_time": 255100.0,
      "text": "Such a mixture is called a suspension."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 255700.0,
      "end_time": 258500.0,
      "text": "This effect of scattering of light is called Tyndall effect."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 259200.0,
      "end_time": 261180.0,
      "text": "Size of particles in a suspension is usually larger than 1000 nm."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 263900.0,
      "end_time": 266100.0,
      "text": "However, these particles eventually settle down."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 266800.0,
      "end_time": 271000.0,
      "text": "After some time, the Tyndall effect may not be observed in suspensions."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 272600.0,
      "end_time": 276000.0,
      "text": "Let us have a look at the 3rd mixture."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 276660.0,
      "end_time": 279200.0,
      "text": "Path of light is visible through the mixture."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 280440.0,
      "end_time": 290700.0,
      "text": "Mixture appears to be Homogeneous, but when observed under a highly powered microscope, it is actually a heterogeneous mixture."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 291400.0,
      "end_time": 295200.0,
      "text": "Such a mixture is called a colloid."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 295800.0,
      "end_time": 299100.0,
      "text": "Size of particles is between 1 nm and 1000 nm."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 300000.0,
      "end_time": 303200.0,
      "text": "In a colloid, the particles never settle down."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 303700.0,
      "end_time": 306900.0,
      "text": "Hence, the Tyndall effect is always observed in colloids."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 330000.0,
      "end_time": 331200.0,
      "text": "The End."
    },
    {
